<p><strong>Super Hearing</strong><br />
 February 9, 2013<br />
 Human hearing analyzes sound significantly better than predicted by conventional theory.<br />
 <img alt="Gray arrow" src="/policy/issues/research-funding/images/gray_arrow_3.gif" border="0" width="6" height="7" hspace="0" /> Article: <em><a href="http://www.gizmodo.com.au/2013/02/how-your-ears-do-maths-better-than-mathematicians/">Gizmodo</a></em><br />
